(91, 1, '2025-12-02 11:24:51', '2025-12-02 04:24:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Whizeva</strong> is a financial business software product by <strong>Ozeva Technology</strong>. <strong>Whizeva</strong> is used to record various types of transactions, such as purchase transactions, sales, inventory, production, as well as the preparation of financial statements in a few simple, flexible, and accurate steps. <strong>Whizeva</strong> is not limited to sales computerization, as it is a comprehensive computerized system consisting of various complete integrated modules, including Accounting, Inventory, Procurement, Production, and Sales, which can be used by various types and scales of businesses. For example, in purchase or sales transactions, these transactions will affect the inventory, debts, and receivables from suppliers or customers. Meanwhile, in cash transactions, there are transactions involving payments or receiving payments that will change the Cash / Bank accounts. <strong>Whizeva</strong> also provides tax invoices, including the Report and Print PPh 21 feature. </p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Whizeva</strong> uses a Client Server Architecture system, which means a computerized model where the client application runs on a desktop or personal computer that accesses information on a server computer (a computer that has the Server application installed). The part of the application that runs on the client is usually used to optimize interaction with the user, while the server provides centralized processing and works in a multi-user environment. The database can be installed on the same computer as the Server application or it can be installed on another computer, as long as that other computer is connected to the server computer (the computer that has the Server application installed). It should be noted, Whizeva is installed on a computer connected to a network; however, if the computer used is not networked, the server, client, and database can be installed on a single computer. This system architecture is a comprehensive system and can be said to encompass everything in every company according to the knowledge and analysis results of the Ozeva Technology team.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Whizeva</strong>&nbsp;didesain untuk bisa digunakan lintas&nbsp;<em>platform (<em>Platform</em>&nbsp;(<em>Environment</em>)&nbsp;<em>Independent</em>). Software</em>&nbsp;ini dapat dijalankan pada berbagai jenis sistem operasi dan berbagai jenis arsitektur komputer. Hal ini sudah teruji dengan menggunakan MS Windows dan Linux OS.&nbsp;<em>Software</em>&nbsp;ini juga menjamin kerahasiaan dan keamanan data informasi yang sudah diinput atau disimpan ke dalam sistem karena semua koneksi&nbsp;<em>database</em>&nbsp;dan&nbsp;<em>password</em>&nbsp;dienkripsi dengan baik. Selain itu,&nbsp;<strong>Whizeva</strong>&nbsp;memiliki pengaturan hak akses/<em>permission</em>&nbsp;terhadap fitur yang ada, sehingga terdapat pembatasan fitur terhadap&nbsp;<em>user</em>&nbsp;sesuai dengan hak akses yang diperbolehkan.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Whizeva: Comprehensive Software for Financial Management', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ozeva-technology-whizeva', '', '', '2025-12-02 11:24:51', '2025-12-02 04:24:51', '', 0, 'https://ozeva.wordpress.com/?p=91', 0, 'post', '', 0),
