(903, 1, '2025-12-04 10:30:39', '2025-12-04 03:30:39', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Ozeva School</strong> is an educational/tutoring unit under Ozeva Technology. Its focus is on helping students learn both school subjects and coding/programming.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"medium\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-medium-font-size\"><strong>What Is Learned at Ozeva School</strong> ?</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>On its official website, it is stated that <a href=\"https://school.ozeva.com/in/home\">Ozeva Schoo</a>l offers several learning programs, including:</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"400\"}},\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-small-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\"><strong>Learning Coding (Programming) </strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong> from beginner to advanced levels to become a programmer.</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3,\"style\":{\"typography\":{\"fontStyle\":\"normal\",\"fontWeight\":\"400\"}},\"fontSize\":\"small\"} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-small-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:400\"><strong>Tutoring for Elementary, Junior High, and High School. The subjects covered include :</strong></h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong></strong> Mathematics<br><strong></strong> Physics<br><strong></strong> Chemistry</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ozeva School is committed to providing the best learning experience through modern methods, experienced teachers, and the latest technological support. With Ozeva School, every student can grow more confidently and achieve their best accomplishments.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Ozeva School: Comprehensive Learning in Coding and Core