(1669, 1, '2025-12-08 01:21:54', '2025-12-08 01:21:54', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Choosing the right <strong>payroll software Indonesia 2026</strong> is no longer an option  it is a strategic necessity for companies in ERP implementation, agriculture/plantation (farm), hotels, restaurants, IT services, distributors/resellers, and all other industries that want accurate, fast, and tax-compliant payroll processes.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-large-font-size\">Why Modern Payroll Software is a Must-Have in Indonesia 2026</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>BPJS Kesehatan &amp; Ketenagakerjaan calculations are increasingly complex</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>PPh 21 final calculation according to the latest Directorate General of Taxes regulations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Multi-branch companies (hotels, restaurants, farms, IT companies) need real-time payroll consolidation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Manual Excel payroll is prone to errors and can result in hundreds of millions in fines</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-large-font-size\">Key Features of the Best Payroll Software 2026  Whizeva Payroll by Ozeva Technology</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Smart Attendance Integration</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Employee attendance data can be entered manually or taken directly from fingerprint/face recognition machines  automatically speeding up timesheet creation. Supports annual leave, sick leave, permit, and absenteeism records.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. Complete Benefits &amp; Deductions</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>All types of allowances (position, transportation, meals, housing) and deductions (late penalties, loans, cooperatives) are recorded automatically and included in salary calculations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. 100% Automatic Salary, Tax &amp; BPJS Calculation</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Whizeva Payroll calculates gross salary  net salary  PPh 21  BPJS Kesehatan &amp; Ketenagakerjaan automatically with 100% compliance with the latest regulations.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":3} -->\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Full Software Customization</h3>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our senior IT consultants will analyze your business needs (whether farm, hotel chain, restaurant group, or IT services company) and customize the payroll system exactly according to your payroll policy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-large-font-size\">Non-Cloud Pricing 2026  Whizeva Payroll (One-Time Payment, Lifetime License)</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:table -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Package</th><th>Standard</th><th>Enterprise (MOST POPULAR)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>Price</strong></td><td>Rp 7.500.000</td><td><strong>Rp 25.000.000</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>License</strong></td><td>1 device, max 50 employees</td><td>2 devices, <strong>UNLIMITED employees</strong></td></tr><tr><td><strong>Additional Device</strong></td><td colspan=\"2\">Rp 2.500.000 / device</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Annual Maintenance</strong></td><td colspan=\"2\">20% per year (includes tax regulation updates)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>Core Features Included</strong></td><td colspan=\"2\"> Employee Data Management<br> Flexible Work Hours &amp; Shift<br> Full Remuneration (allowances + deductions)<br> Multi Currency Support<br> PPh 21 &amp; BPJS Auto Calculation<br> Hundreds of Professional Reports<br> Multi-User Access<br> Import/Export Excel<br> Automatic Backup &amp; Restore<br> Free Software Customization<br> Free Installation &amp; Training<br> <strong>Lifetime Warranty &amp; Support</strong></td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<!-- /wp:table -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-large-font-size\">Perfect for All Industries</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>ERP Companies</strong>  seamless integration with existing ERP modules</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Plantations / Farms</strong>  daily worker payroll &amp; harvest bonus management</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Hotels &amp; Resorts</strong>  service charge distribution &amp; multi-shift handling</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Restaurants &amp; F&amp;B Chains</strong>  tip &amp; overtime calculations</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>IT Services &amp; Software Houses</strong>  project-based allowance management</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li><strong>Resellers &amp; Distributors</strong>  sales commission auto-calculation</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading {\"fontSize\":\"large\"} -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-large-font-size\">Conclusion: Stop Using Excel for Payroll in 2026</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>One small calculation error can cost millions in tax fines or employee dissatisfaction. More than <strong>8,400 companies</strong> across Indonesia (from small resellers to large hotel chains and plantations) have trusted Ozeva Technologys solutions since 2008.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://ozeva.com/payroll\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get Free Consultation &amp; Demo Now  ozeva.com/payroll</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>Copyright  2008-2025 Ozeva Technology. All Rights Reserved.</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Best Payroll Software Indonesia 2026: Complete Guide for ERP, Farm, Hotel, Restaurant, IT Services &amp; Reseller Businesses', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1428-revision-v1', '', '', '2025-12-08 01:21:54', '2025-12-08 01:21:54', '', 1428, 'http://ozeva.com.test:8000/?p=1669', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
